'''Salome Nyirarukundo''' (yavutse 20 Ukuboza 1997) ni umukinnyi [[Rwanda|w'umunyarwanda]] wiruka intera ndende.Yitabiriye imikino Olempike ya 2016 yabereye i [[Rio de Janeiro]], muri metero 10,000 z'abagore, arangiza ku mwanya wa 27 akoresheje 32: 07.80. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20160806071912/https://www.rio2016.com/en/athlete/sallome-nyirarukundo</ref><ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/where-marathoner-nyirarukundo</ref>

== Amarushanwa ==

=== 2017 - 2018 ===
Nyirarukundo nawe ni umukinnyi wiruka marato wamenyereye, kandi yitabiriye amarushanwa akomeye. Yashyizeho igihe cyiza kuri Marathon ya Montreal (2:28:02). Yatsinze amarushanwa menshi mu Ntara ya Québec, harimo na marato ya Rimouski<ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/rwandan-athlete-nyirarukundo-wins-monreal</ref>.

=== 2019 ===
Nyirarukundo yagize akazi muri 2019. Mu isiganwa rya Around The Bay 30Km, yaje ku mwanya wa 3 nyuma y'abakinnyi b'indashyikirwa, nubwo yayoboye ibirometero 15 by'isiganwa. Yatsinze isiganwa rya 10km St-Laurent akoresheje iminota 34. Yatwaye umwanya wa kabiri kuri 5k du Lac-Beauport kandi yatsindiye Lévis Half-Marathon mugihe cya 1h 13 min 59 s. Yarangije ku mwanya wa 4 muri Marato ya Ottawa akoresheje 2 h 30 min hanyuma akora izindi 10km muri lululemon Toronto muminota 34,  Hanyuma, yagize izindi ntsinzi ebyiri muri 10km, iya La Baie n'iya [[Kanada]] yo gusiganwa ku magare. Nyuma yibyo, yitabiriye Marathon ya Rimouski<ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/nyirarukundoto-stay-out-for-five-months</ref> .
